			p
				u
					strong Moderators can&nbsp;still skip some, or all actions&nbsp;based on the specific case, history of the player, and if there&rsquo;s malicious intent.
			p Punishments get progressively harsher as the offender repeats the infraction, ultimately resulting in a ban.
